name: Tackle
description: User flings self at target. Extra damage inflicted with certain armours. Will hurt itself slightly.

name: Body Slam
description: User hurls self at target. Extra damage inflicted with certain armours. Will hurt itself.

name: Strike
description: User swings a limb at target. Extra damage inflicted with certain limbs.

name: Jab
description: User thrusts a limb at target. Extra damage inflicted with certain limbs.

name: Bludgeon
description: User bashes a target with a limb. Extra damage inflicted with certain limbs. Will hurt itself.

name: Slash
description: User swings a sharp blade at target.

name: Stab
description: User thrusts a sharp point at target.
